  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201503/bcb0b2ee3c9c4a019ceb73e8ed9548bd.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">去年新闻发言人吕新华以一句&ldquo;你懂得&rdquo;引爆关注。在今年的全国政协十二届三次会议新闻发布会上，他的一句&ldquo;大家都很任性&rdquo;再次让人印象深刻，更是难倒了在场的英语翻译，她忙和发言人沟通，询问&ldquo;大家都很任性&rdquo;的含义。</span></p>\n<div>\n\t最后她给出的翻译是：<strong>&ldquo;So we can be said to be capricious in fighting against corruption,and we are entitled to be so.&rdquo;</strong>这种补充说明的处理技巧在翻译中很常见。</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong>capricious&nbsp;</strong></div>\n<div>\n\t<strong>adj.反覆无常的, 任性的, 善变的</strong></div>\n<div>\n\t柯林斯给出的解释是:Someone who is capricious often changes their mind unexpectedly.</div>\n<div>\n\t这个词语指人的时候，通常更偏向于反复无常，变化莫测。</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t辣么，怎么理解&ldquo;任性&rdquo;这个词语？快来看看任性的网友们都有哪些招儿吧。</div>\n<div>\n\t1、Follow your heart!（好吧，我能说&ldquo;怂&rdquo;也是从心所欲不逾矩咩~）</div>\n<div>\n\t2、任性就是just do it（想做就做），股市就是just buy it（买买买）；打老虎就是just beat it（呃&hellip;&hellip;这个也是蛮神准的）</div>\n<div>\n\t3、We just enjoy and do it!（喜欢这么做！也是蛮任性的）</div>\n<div>\n\t最后，来一个牛掰的：</div>\n<div>\n\t4、Everyone is very duang（每个人都很duang啊，想加特技就加特技）</div>\n<div>\n\tduang~搜待斯乃。</div>\n<div>\n\tEveryone is duang crying~</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p722553/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p722553\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p722333/\">一张图记住口语常用动词词组</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p721724/\">心理医生建议：五十度灰的正确观看方式</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p722282/\">外媒: duang到底是个什么鬼火成这样！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujian